'''小港'''（Marina Piccola，又名''Marina di Mulo''）<ref name="Baedeker1903">{{cite book|last=Baedeker |first=Karl|title=Italy: Southern Italy and Sicily, with excursions to the Lipari islands, Malta, Sardinia, Tunis and Corfu. 13th rev. ed. 1900|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=9ck9AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA157|accessdate= 2012-07-05|edition=Public domain|year=1903|publisher=K. Baedeker|pages=157–}}</ref> 位于[[卡普里岛|卡普里岛]]南侧，附近东南海中有[[卡普里奇岩|卡普里奇岩]]<ref name="JepsonSoriano2011">{{cite book|last1=Jepson|first1=Tim|last2=Soriano|first2=Tino|title=National Geographic Traveler: Naples and Southern Italy, 2nd Edition|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=ds-7ZMz7yCUC&pg=PA116|accessdate= 2012-07-04|date=2011-01-18|publisher=National Geographic Books|isbn=978-1-4262-0710-5|pages=116–}}</ref>。[[克虏伯路|克虏伯路]]是一条历史悠久的盘山小道，从小港通往[[圣雅各伯修道院|圣雅各伯修道院]]和[[奥古斯都花园|奥古斯都花园]]地区 <ref name="capri.it">{{cite web|url=http://www.capri.com/en/s/augustus-gardens-via-krupp|title=Capri: Augustus Gardens - Via Krupp|accessdate=2010-10-11|archive-date=2010-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100904041754/http://www.capri.com/en/s/augustus-gardens-via-krupp|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。小港早在[[奥古斯都|奥古斯都]]和[[提贝里乌斯|提贝里乌斯]]已经使用，早于[[大港_(卡普里岛)|大港]]<ref name="DickensAinsworth1854">{{cite book|last1=Dickens|first1=Charles|last2=Ainsworth|first2=William Harrison|last3=Smith|first3=Albert|title=Bentley's miscellany|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=XuERAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA39|accessdate=2012-07-05|edition=Public domain|year=1854|publisher=Richard Bentley|pages=39–}}</ref>。

